{"tid":1313932,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：好掛住佢地，真係非常非常之掛住佢地","createTime":"2019-07-14T03:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:33:22.000Z","uid":80336,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6960f2f242972996d3a98341a6e8b7cea7f84d","tid":1313932,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-1RDpzdUPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds-1RDpzdUPA&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=bd3ff585\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-1RDpzdUPA</a><br />\n天琦係我政治啟蒙，都係我覺得佢係歷史上最負責任既一位從政者，<br />\n呢2個月勇武派好辛苦衝去前線，我好少去，只係612，我廢易累<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係係屋企睇下政治片，睇下新聞，幫手係社交網站宣揚依家咩事<br />\n我工作身份既性質係和理非，但好多做左呢一行既都出左去幫手<br />\n而我只能夠盡我能力係工作環境入邊同其他同事宣揚勇武既理念<br />\n同埋對住我D客講立會果班唔係暴徒，盡左力<br />\n而今日我開YOUTUBE 呢條片，睇到最後聽到佢呢句，我喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位勇武派我知好辛苦，但要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5c5ac6b01d3424c5cdc5e4fe9e37a91542189a","tid":1313932,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"全部同我入黎！教你下一步點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}